folder: Bedford Avenue & Martense Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
2164 Bedford Ave., west side, at, adjoining and south of Martense Street. The view also shows 90-92 Martense Street, south side, at, adjoining, and south of Bedford Ave. The view shows a frame house at 90 Martense Street. Also shown is the Second Reformed Dutch Church of Flatbush.

March 29, 1932

F.L. Sperr.
